Package prng.collector

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AWTEntropy
    An entropy collector that sample small random areas of the connected graphical devices.
    DaemonThreadFactory
    A creator of daemon threads for the PRNG background processes.
    EntropyCollector
    Entropy source that can pull entropy from some source on a regular basis feeds into Fortuna.
    EntropyInputStream
    A utility input stream where the contents of the stream contribute to system entropy.
    EntropyOutputStream
    An utility output stream where the contents of the stream contribute to system entropy.
    FreeMemoryEntropy
    Use the amount of free memory available to the VM at a given time as a source of entropy
    GarbageCollectorEntropy
    Use the amount of time spent collecting garbage as a source of entropy
    HeapEntropy
    Collect entropy from how objects are allocated on the heap.
    InstantEntropy
    Attempts to create useful entropy from nothing.
    InstantEntropy.Counter
    Count of ready entropy blocks
    InstantEntropy.Holder
    Holder for some entropy that will be derived at some point in the future.
    InstantEntropy.Result
    A seed source that holds the result of entropy generation and releases it as it is requested.
    SchedulingEntropy
    Use the amount of time between calls as a source of entropy
    ThreadTimeEntropy
    Use current thread CPU time and User time as a source of entropy
Author:
Simon Greatrix
